was in the rain and we all stuck together to celebrate this shared humanity, and I believe in this.\\\"\", \"from\": 2541, \"to\": 2650, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Everyone\", \"from\": 2541, \"to\": 2549}, {\"ngram\": \"the rain\", \"from\": 2557, \"to\": 2565}, {\"ngram\": \"this shared humanity\", \"from\": 2605, \"to\": 2625}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Paris 2024 president Tony Estanguet, meanwhile, pointed out the 6800 athletes who took part would have been caught under the same deluge in a stadium, and said many took advantage of the option provided for them to leaving early after the flotilla was done.\", \"from\": 2652, \"to\": 2909, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2652, \"end\": 2662, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.82709989538857e-20, \"text\": \"Paris 2024\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 2673, \"end\": 2687, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tony_Estanguet\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Tony Estanguet\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tony_Estanguet\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tony_Estanguet\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the 6800 athletes\", \"from\": 2712, \"to\": 2729}, {\"ngram\": \"part\", \"from\": 2739, \"to\": 2743}, {\"ngram\": \"the same deluge\", \"from\": 2773, \"to\": 2788}, {\"ngram\": \"a stadium\", \"from\": 2792, \"to\": 2801}, {\"ngram\": \"advantage\", \"from\": 2822, \"to\": 2831}, {\"ngram\": \"the option\", \"from\": 2835, \"to\": 2845}, {\"ngram\": \"the flotilla\", \"from\": 2887, \"to\": 2899}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Ceremonies director Thierry Reboul revealed the weather resulted in his team \\\"taking decisions almost by the second.\", \"from\": 2911, \"to\": 3027, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2931, \"end\": 2938, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Augustin_Thierry\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.908141192503112e-21, \"text\": \"Thierry\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Augustin_Thierry\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Augustin_Thierry\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the weather\", \"from\": 2955, \"to\": 2966}, {\"ngram\": \"his team\", \"from\": 2979, \"to\": 2987}, {\"ngram\": \"decisions\", \"from\": 2996, \"to\": 3005}, {\"ngram\": \"the second\", \"from\": 3016, \"to\": 3026}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We had to constantly change the show, deciding whether or not we could put some artists on the rooftops of the city.\\\"\", \"from\": 3028, \"to\": 3145, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the show\", \"from\": 3056, \"to\": 3064}, {\"ngram\": \"some artists\", \"from\": 3103, \"to\": 3115}, {\"ngram\": \"the rooftops\", \"from\": 3119, \"to\": 3131}, {\"ngram\": \"the city\", \"from\": 3135, \"to\": 3143}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Not a single artist decided not to do something, not a single one decided to stop.\", \"from\": 3147, \"to\": 3230, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Not a single artist\", \"from\": 3148, \"to\": 3167}, {\"ngram\": \"something\", \"from\": 3186, \"to\": 3195}, {\"ngram\": \"a single one\", \"from\": 3201, \"to\": 3213}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I want to congratulate them for being so courageous, especially our singer on the rooftop of the Grand Palais and also Celine Dion, who never, ever actually wanted to do that anywhere else but on the Eiffel Tower.\\\"\", \"from\": 3231, \"to\": 3445, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3350, \"end\": 3361, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Celine_Dion\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.327370004080746e-33, \"text\": \"Celine Dion\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Celine_Dion\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Celine_Dion\"}]